description: Generates a presigned download URL for the specified release of the mobile SDK. The mobile SDK is not generally available. Customers who have access to the mobile SDK can use it to establish and manage WAF tokens for use in HTTP(S) requests from a mobile device to WAF. For more information, see WAF client application integration in the WAF Developer Guide.

parameters.name: ReleaseVersion
parameters.description: The release version. For the latest available version, specify LATEST.

nested_items.name: Url
nested_items.description: The presigned download URL for the specified SDK release.
